       Also online under an open copyright.</p>
  </dd>

  <dt>
    <span class="subhead"><a
href="http://questioncopyright.org/promise"
    ><b><i>The Promise of a Post-Copyright World</i></b></a></span>
  </dt>
  <dd>
    <p>An article about expanding open source principles beyond the
       software field.<br/>
       Online under an open copyright.</p>
  </dd>

  <dt>
    <span class="subhead"><a
