  </dt>
  <dd>
    <p>An article at O'ReillyNet that explains free software to the
       general reader.<br/>
       Online under an open copyright.</p>
  </dd>

  <dt>
    <span class="subhead"><a
    href="http://www.gnu.org/philosophy/why-audio-format-matters.html"
