       for the Free Software Foundation.<br/>
       Online under an open copyright.</p>
  </dd>

  <dt>
    <span class="subhead"><b><i>Linux Bible</i></b>
                            <i>(two chapters)</i></span>
  </dt>
  <dd>
    <p>Wrote the chapters on Emacs and shell customization in
       the <i>Linux User's Guide</i>, later published in the
       <i>Linux Bible</i> from Yggdrasil Computing,
       ISBN&nbsp;1-88360-10-X.</p>
  </dd>

</dl>
